2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper focuses on designing a dynamic maneuver for a UAV-enabled communication system, which involves networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a reinforcement learning-based approach for online maneuver design, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with designing a control system for a UAV-enabled communication system, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper deals with designing a dynamic maneuver for a UAV, which falls under the domain of robotics.
